OL,3,C'Our kids aren't a budget': The mum-of-
OL,4,Cthree's fight as SEND rules are
OL,5,Crewritten
OL,7,FA mother who has spent years battling
OL,8,Ffor her children's education says she
OL,9,Ffears a radical government overhaul of
OL,10,Fthe Special Educational Needs and
OL,11,FDisabilities (SEND) system could see
OL,12,Fchildren "put into a budget" rather
OL,13,Fthan receiving the support they need.
OL,15,FThe government today unveiled its
OL,16,FEvery Child Achieving and Thriving
OL,17,Fwhite paper, promising to end a one
OL,18,Fsize fits all system that Education
OL,19,FSecretary Bridget Phillipson admits
OL,20,Fhas "traumatised too many families."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
