FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1771934580
OL,3,C'Our kids aren't a budget': The mum-of-
OL,4,Cthree's fight as SEND rules are
OL,5,Crewritten
OL,7,FCentral to the reforms is a new legal
OL,8,Fright for over a million children to
OL,9,Fhave an Individual Support Plan (ISP).
OL,10,FFor those with more complex needs, the
OL,11,Fexisting Education, Health and Care
OL,12,FPlans (EHCPs) will be retained but
OL,13,Fimproved through digitisation and a
OL,14,Fnew national framework.
OL,16,FFor Aimee Bradley, the news is met
OL,17,Fwith more than a little skepticism.
OL,18,FAimee's life is defined by the fight
OL,19,Fthe government now claims it wants to
OL,20,Fend.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1771934580
OL,3,C'Our kids aren't a budget': The mum-of-
OL,4,Cthree's fight as SEND rules are
OL,5,Crewritten
OL,7,FShe has three children with additional
OL,8,Fneeds: Autumn, 13, who has autism and
OL,9,FADHD; Ashton, 7, who has autism and
OL,10,Flearning difficulties; and four-year-
OL,11,Fold Blake, who is autistic and has
OL,12,Fglobal developmental delay.
OL,14,F"It's about having that correct
OL,15,Fplacement for a child so they are
OL,16,Fgoing to flourish," Aimee told ITV
OL,17,FMeridian. "The biggest worry is being
OL,18,Fput into a school that won't be able
OL,19,Fto help your child grow.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1771934580
OL,3,C'Our kids aren't a budget': The mum-of-
OL,4,Cthree's fight as SEND rules are
OL,5,Crewritten
OL,7,F"I'm worried that our children are
OL,8,Fgoing to be put into a budget rather
OL,9,Fthan having an education that is put
OL,10,Faround them. Fitting them into a
OL,11,Fbudget section, rather than having the
OL,12,Fsupport in place no matter how much it
OL,13,Fcosts."
OL,15,FThe government insists no child will
OL,16,Fbe left behind during the transition.
OL,17,FA triple lock of protections has been
OL,18,Fannounced:
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1771934580
OL,3,C'Our kids aren't a budget': The mum-of-
OL,4,Cthree's fight as SEND rules are
OL,5,Crewritten
OL,7,FHowever, Aimee is particularly
OL,8,Fconcerned for her eldest, Autumn, who
OL,9,Fis approaching the jump to post-16
OL,10,Feducation.
OL,12,F"She's a mainstream student with an
OL,13,FEHCP," Aimee explains. "Without that
OL,14,Fsupport, she wouldn't be able to go to
OL,15,Fschool. She wouldn't be able to
OL,16,Fsurvive, get through the door, or even
OL,17,Ffunction.
OL,19,F"How is her plan going to look in the
OL,20,Fnew system? Will she continue to get
OL,21,Fthat targeted support in college?"
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1771934580
OL,3,C'Our kids aren't a budget': The mum-of-
OL,4,Cthree's fight as SEND rules are
OL,5,Crewritten
OL,7,FThe Education Secretary has pledged
OL,8,F#1.6 billion in inclusion grants and
OL,9,F#3.7 billion to create 60,000 more
OL,10,Fspecialist places.
OL,12,F"The SEND system designed ten years
OL,13,Fago for a small number of children is
OL,14,Fnow broken," said Bridget Phillipson.
OL,15,F"Today's plans will take children with
OL,16,FSEND from sidelined and excluded to
OL,17,Fseen, heard and included."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1771934580
OL,3,C'Our kids aren't a budget': The mum-of-
OL,4,Cthree's fight as SEND rules are
OL,5,Crewritten
OL,7,FBut for Aimee's youngest, Blake, the
OL,8,F"broken" system is a current reality.
OL,9,FDespite his needs leaning toward
OL,10,Fspecialist provision, he was recently
OL,11,Fgiven a mainstream placement for
OL,12,FSeptember. Seven schools have already
OL,13,Fsaid they cannot meet his needs.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1771934580
OL,3,C'Our kids aren't a budget': The mum-of-
OL,4,Cthree's fight as SEND rules are
OL,5,Crewritten
OL,7,F"I'm one of those parents that, again,
OL,8,Fis having to go to tribunal," Aimee
OL,9,Fsays. "My son Ashton was also given
OL,10,Fmainstream when he was non-verbal.
OL,11,FHe's now in an amazing school, he's
OL,12,Fthriving and talking. That's why
OL,13,Fgetting Blake the right placement is
OL,14,Fso important."
OL,16,FWhile the government says the new
OL,17,Fsystem will reduce the need for legal
OL,18,Fbattles, Aimee remains unconvinced by
OL,19,Fthe lack of detail for early years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,419,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1771934580
OL,3,C'Our kids aren't a budget': The mum-of-
OL,4,Cthree's fight as SEND rules are
OL,5,Crewritten
OL,7,F"I've not seen anything about what
OL,8,Fhappens before school," she says.
OL,9,F"They say those with 'complex needs'
OL,10,Fwill be given spaces automatically.
OL,11,FBut what is complex? Who deems what is
OL,12,Fcomplex?"
OL,14,FUnder the new plans, the SEND Tribunal
OL,15,Fwill remain as a "legal backstop," but
OL,16,Fthe government hopes improved
OL,17,Fmediation and the new statutory ISPs
OL,18,Fwill stop families ever needing to
OL,19,Freach that stage.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
